# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Keep git metadata and ignore file itself.
!.gitignore
!README.md

# Public, consumer-facing artifacts.
!ChessSansVariableFont.ttf
!Format — OTF/
!Format — OTF/**
!Format — TTF/
!Format — TTF/**
!Format — WOFF/
!Format — WOFF/**
!Format — WOFF2/
!Format — WOFF2/**
!Rounded — OTF/
!Rounded — OTF/**

# Ignore nested folder named like the repo (legacy/accidental).
ChessSans/

# Exclude OS junk and shortcuts even inside public folders.
**/.DS_Store
**/._*
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini
*.lnk
